    "Adds a “Mark car” button to the ride screen so you can tag the moment a vehicle passes — handy for checking radar timing. Most riders can leave this off." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de-DE" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Fügt dem Fahrtbildschirm eine Schaltfläche „Auto markieren“ hinzu, um den Moment einer Vorbeifahrt zu markieren — praktisch zum Prüfen des Radar-Timings. Die meisten können das ausgeschaltet lassen."
          }
        },
        "en-GB" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Adds a “Mark car” button to the ride screen so you can tag the moment a vehicle passes — handy for checking radar timing. Most riders can leave this off."
          }
        },
        "en-US" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Adds a “Mark car” button to the ride screen so you can tag the moment a vehicle passes — handy for checking radar timing. Most riders can leave this off."
          }
        },
        "es-ES" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Añade un botón « Marcar coche » a la pantalla de ruta para marcar cuándo pasa un vehículo: útil para comprobar el sincronismo del radar. La mayoría puede dejarlo desactivado."
          }
        },
        "fr-FR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ajoute un bouton « Marquer voiture » à l'écran de sortie pour marquer le passage d'un véhicule — pratique pour vérifier le timing du radar. La plupart des cyclistes peuvent le laisser désactivé."
          }
        },
        "it-IT" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Aggiunge un pulsante « Segna auto » alla schermata dell'uscita per segnare il momento di un passaggio — utile per verificare i tempi del radar. La maggior parte può lasciarlo disattivato."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Adds a Junction tile to the ride screen showing the next intersection ahead — its layout and the distance to it, counting down as you approach. Road data around your route is fetched from OpenStreetMap while this is on, which sends your approximate location to OpenStreetMap's servers. Nothing is sent while it's off." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de-DE" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Fügt dem Fahrbildschirm eine Kreuzungs-Kachel hinzu, die die nächste Kreuzung voraus zeigt – ihre Form und die Entfernung dazu, die beim Näherkommen herunterzählt. Solange dies aktiviert ist, werden Straßendaten rund um deine Route von OpenStreetMap geladen; dabei wird dein ungefährer Standort an die Server von OpenStreetMap gesendet. Ist es deaktiviert, wird nichts gesendet."
          }
        },
        "en-GB" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Adds a Junction tile to the ride screen showing the next intersection ahead — its layout and the distance to it, counting down as you approach. Road data around your route is fetched from OpenStreetMap while this is on, which sends your approximate location to OpenStreetMap's servers. Nothing is sent while it's off."
          }
        },
        "en-US" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Adds a Junction tile to the ride screen showing the next intersection ahead — its layout and the distance to it, counting down as you approach. Road data around your route is fetched from OpenStreetMap while this is on, which sends your approximate location to OpenStreetMap's servers. Nothing is sent while it's off."
          }
        },
        "es-ES" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Añade a la pantalla de marcha un recuadro de Cruce que muestra el próximo cruce: su forma y la distancia hasta él, en cuenta atrás a medida que te acercas. Mientras está activado, los datos de carreteras alrededor de tu ruta se descargan de OpenStreetMap, lo que envía tu ubicación aproximada a los servidores de OpenStreetMap. Con la opción desactivada no se envía nada."
          }
        },
        "fr-FR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ajoute une tuile Intersection à l’écran de conduite montrant la prochaine intersection – sa forme et la distance qui vous en sépare, décomptée à mesure que vous approchez. Tant que cette option est activée, les données routières autour de votre itinéraire sont récupérées depuis OpenStreetMap, ce qui envoie votre position approximative aux serveurs d’OpenStreetMap. Rien n’est envoyé quand elle est désactivée."
          }
        },
        "it-IT" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Aggiunge alla schermata di guida un riquadro Incrocio che mostra il prossimo incrocio – la sua forma e la distanza, con conto alla rovescia mentre ti avvicini. Finché è attivo, i dati stradali intorno al tuo percorso vengono scaricati da OpenStreetMap, inviando la tua posizione approssimativa ai server di OpenStreetMap. Quando è disattivato non viene inviato nulla."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Adds a map button to the ride screen for planning and picking routes. Plan by tapping start and waypoints on a map — the path snaps to quiet roads and cycle paths, and loops back to the start unless you choose a separate finish. While following a route it appears in the radar panel whenever the road behind is clear, and the Junction tile points the way; pick a route while away from it and CycleHUD also plots a lead-in to the start. Planning and the lead-in send the needed points to the BRouter routing service (brouter.de, OpenStreetMap data); saved routes stay on your device and can be shared as files." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de-DE" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Fügt dem Fahrbildschirm eine Karten-Taste zum Planen und Auswählen von Routen hinzu. Plane, indem du Start und Wegpunkte auf einer Karte antippst – der Weg folgt ruhigen Straßen und Radwegen und führt zurück zum Start, sofern du kein separates Ziel wählst. Beim Folgen einer Route erscheint sie im Radarfeld, solange die Straße hinter dir frei ist, und die Kreuzungs-Kachel zeigt die Richtung; wählst du eine Route abseits von ihr, plant CycleHUD zusätzlich eine Zufahrt zum Start. Planung und Zufahrt senden die nötigen Punkte an den Routing-Dienst BRouter (brouter.de, OpenStreetMap-Daten); gespeicherte Routen bleiben auf deinem Gerät und lassen sich als Dateien teilen."
          }
        },
        "en-GB" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Adds a map button to the ride screen for planning and picking routes. Plan by tapping start and waypoints on a map — the path snaps to quiet roads and cycle paths, and loops back to the start unless you choose a separate finish. While following a route it appears in the radar panel whenever the road behind is clear, and the Junction tile points the way; pick a route while away from it and CycleHUD also plots a lead-in to the start. Planning and the lead-in send the needed points to the BRouter routing service (brouter.de, OpenStreetMap data); saved routes stay on your device and can be shared as files."
          }
        },
        "en-US" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Adds a map button to the ride screen for planning and picking routes. Plan by tapping start and waypoints on a map — the path snaps to quiet roads and cycle paths, and loops back to the start unless you choose a separate finish. While following a route it appears in the radar panel whenever the road behind is clear, and the Junction tile points the way; pick a route while away from it and CycleHUD also plots a lead-in to the start. Planning and the lead-in send the needed points to the BRouter routing service (brouter.de, OpenStreetMap data); saved routes stay on your device and can be shared as files."
          }
        },
        "es-ES" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Añade un botón de mapa a la pantalla de marcha para planificar y elegir rutas. Planifica tocando la salida y puntos intermedios en un mapa: el trazado sigue carreteras tranquilas y carriles bici, y vuelve a la salida salvo que elijas una meta distinta. Mientras sigues una ruta, esta aparece en el panel del radar siempre que la carretera de detrás esté despejada, y el recuadro de Cruce indica la dirección; si eliges una ruta lejos de ella, CycleHUD también traza un acceso hasta la salida. La planificación y ese acceso envían los puntos necesarios al servicio de rutas BRouter (brouter.de, datos de OpenStreetMap); las rutas guardadas permanecen en tu dispositivo y pueden compartirse como archivos."
          }
        },
        "fr-FR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ajoute un bouton carte à l’écran de conduite pour planifier et choisir des itinéraires. Planifiez en touchant le départ et des étapes sur une carte – le tracé suit les routes calmes et les pistes cyclables, et revient au départ sauf si vous choisissez une arrivée distincte. Pendant le suivi, l’itinéraire s’affiche dans le panneau radar tant que la route derrière est dégagée, et la tuile Intersection indique la direction ; si vous choisissez un itinéraire loin de celui-ci, CycleHUD trace aussi un accès jusqu’au départ. La planification et cet accès envoient les points nécessaires au service de calcul d’itinéraire BRouter (brouter.de, données OpenStreetMap) ; les itinéraires enregistrés restent sur votre appareil et peuvent être partagés sous forme de fichiers."
          }
        },
        "it-IT" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Aggiunge alla schermata di guida un pulsante mappa per pianificare e scegliere i percorsi. Pianifica toccando partenza e tappe su una mappa – il tracciato segue strade tranquille e piste ciclabili e torna alla partenza, a meno che tu non scelga un arrivo diverso. Mentre segui un percorso, questo appare nel pannello radar finché la strada dietro è libera, e il riquadro Incrocio indica la direzione; se attivi un percorso lontano da esso, CycleHUD traccia anche un avvicinamento alla partenza. La pianificazione e l’avvicinamento inviano i punti necessari al servizio di routing BRouter (brouter.de, dati OpenStreetMap); i percorsi salvati restano sul tuo dispositivo e possono essere condivisi come file."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Adds one example ride (a Central Park loop with a route, vehicles on the map and vehicle passes) to Previous rides, so you can see how a completed ride looks. Swipe to delete it there when you're done." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de-DE" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Fügt eine Beispielfahrt (eine Runde durch den Central Park mit Route, Fahrzeugen auf der Karte und Vorbeifahrten) zu „Frühere Fahrten“ hinzu, damit du siehst, wie eine abgeschlossene Fahrt aussieht. Dort zum Löschen wischen, wenn du fertig bist."
          }
        },
        "en-GB" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Adds one example ride (a Central Park loop with a route, vehicles on the map and vehicle passes) to Previous rides, so you can see how a completed ride looks. Swipe to delete it there when you're done."
          }
        },
        "en-US" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Adds one example ride (a Central Park loop with a route, vehicles on the map and vehicle passes) to Previous rides, so you can see how a completed ride looks. Swipe to delete it there when you're done."
          }
        },
        "es-ES" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Añade una ruta de ejemplo (una vuelta a Central Park con recorrido, vehículos en el mapa y adelantamientos) a Rutas anteriores, para ver cómo se ve una ruta completada. Desliza para eliminarla cuando termines."
          }
        },
        "fr-FR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ajoute une sortie d'exemple (une boucle de Central Park avec itinéraire, véhicules sur la carte et dépassements) aux Sorties précédentes, pour voir à quoi ressemble une sortie terminée. Balayez pour la supprimer ensuite."
          }
        },
        "it-IT" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Aggiunge un'uscita di esempio (un giro a Central Park con percorso, veicoli sulla mappa e sorpassi) a Uscite precedenti, così vedi com'è un'uscita completata. Scorri per eliminarla quando hai finito."
          }
        }
      }
    },
