    "Backs up your rides, routes and ghosts to your own iCloud and keeps a new phone in step. Everything stays in your personal iCloud Drive — no accounts and no CycleHUD servers. When two devices hold the same route, the faster ghost wins." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de-DE" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Sichert deine Fahrten, Routen und Geister in deiner eigenen iCloud und hält ein neues Telefon auf dem gleichen Stand. Alles bleibt in deinem persönlichen iCloud Drive – keine Konten und keine CycleHUD-Server. Haben zwei Geräte dieselbe Route, gewinnt der schnellere Geist."
          }
        },
        "en-GB" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Backs up your rides, routes and ghosts to your own iCloud and keeps a new phone in step. Everything stays in your personal iCloud Drive — no accounts and no CycleHUD servers. When two devices hold the same route, the faster ghost wins."
          }
        },
        "en-US" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Backs up your rides, routes and ghosts to your own iCloud and keeps a new phone in step. Everything stays in your personal iCloud Drive — no accounts and no CycleHUD servers. When two devices hold the same route, the faster ghost wins."
          }
        },
        "es-ES" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Guarda tus salidas, rutas y fantasmas en tu propio iCloud y mantiene un teléfono nuevo al día. Todo permanece en tu iCloud Drive personal: sin cuentas y sin servidores de CycleHUD. Si dos dispositivos tienen la misma ruta, gana el fantasma más rápido."
          }
        },
        "fr-FR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Sauvegarde vos sorties, itinéraires et fantômes dans votre propre iCloud et garde un nouveau téléphone à jour. Tout reste dans votre iCloud Drive personnel – pas de comptes ni de serveurs CycleHUD. Si deux appareils ont le même itinéraire, le fantôme le plus rapide gagne."
          }
        },
        "it-IT" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Salva le tue uscite, i percorsi e i fantasmi nel tuo iCloud e mantiene aggiornato un nuovo telefono. Tutto resta nel tuo iCloud Drive personale: nessun account e nessun server CycleHUD. Se due dispositivi hanno lo stesso percorso, vince il fantasma più veloce."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Based on your rides on similar terrain." : {
