    "CycleHUD can't save your rides as workouts. Open the Health app → Sharing → Apps → CycleHUD and allow Workouts and Active Energy — or turn off “Save rides as workouts”." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de-DE" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD kann deine Fahrten nicht als Trainings speichern. Öffne die Health-App → Bereitstellung → Apps → CycleHUD und erlaube Trainings und Aktive Energie — oder deaktiviere „Fahrten als Trainings speichern“."
          }
        },
        "en-GB" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD can't save your rides as workouts. Open the Health app → Sharing → Apps → CycleHUD and allow Workouts and Active Energy — or turn off “Save rides as workouts”."
          }
        },
        "en-US" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD can't save your rides as workouts. Open the Health app → Sharing → Apps → CycleHUD and allow Workouts and Active Energy — or turn off “Save rides as workouts”."
          }
        },
        "es-ES" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD no puede guardar tus rutas como entrenamientos. Abre la app Salud → Compartir → Apps → CycleHUD y permite Entrenamientos y Energía activa, o desactiva « Guardar rutas como entrenamientos »."
          }
        },
        "fr-FR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD ne peut pas enregistrer vos sorties comme entraînements. Ouvrez l'app Santé → Partage → Apps → CycleHUD et autorisez Entraînements et Énergie active — ou désactivez « Enregistrer les sorties comme entraînements »."
          }
        },
        "it-IT" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD non può salvare le uscite come allenamenti. Apri l'app Salute → Condivisione → App → CycleHUD e consenti Allenamenti ed Energia attiva — oppure disattiva « Salva le uscite come allenamenti »."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "CycleHUD is a personal quality-of-life cycling HUD built around the Coospo TR70 rear radar. Vehicles behind you appear on a clear radar lane with Apple Watch wrist alerts, and each ride is saved as an Apple Health workout. Also works with Garmin Varia–compatible radars and standard CSC speed/cadence sensors." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de-DE" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD ist ein persönliches Komfort-HUD fürs Radfahren rund um das Coospo-TR70-Heckradar. Fahrzeuge hinter dir erscheinen auf einer klaren Radar-Spur mit Apple-Watch-Warnungen, und jede Fahrt wird als Apple-Health-Training gespeichert. Funktioniert auch mit Garmin-Varia-kompatiblen Radargeräten und Standard-CSC-Geschwindigkeits-/Trittfrequenzsensoren."
          }
        },
        "en-GB" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD is a personal quality-of-life cycling HUD built around the Coospo TR70 rear radar. Vehicles behind you appear on a clear radar lane with Apple Watch wrist alerts, and each ride is saved as an Apple Health workout. Also works with Garmin Varia–compatible radars and standard CSC speed/cadence sensors."
          }
        },
        "en-US" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD is a personal quality-of-life cycling HUD built around the Coospo TR70 rear radar. Vehicles behind you appear on a clear radar lane with Apple Watch wrist alerts, and each ride is saved as an Apple Health workout. Also works with Garmin Varia–compatible radars and standard CSC speed/cadence sensors."
          }
        },
        "es-ES" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD es un HUD personal para ciclismo basado en el radar trasero Coospo TR70. Los vehículos detrás de ti aparecen en un carril de radar claro con avisos en el Apple Watch, y cada ruta se guarda como entrenamiento de Apple Salud. También funciona con radares compatibles con Garmin Varia y sensores de velocidad/cadencia CSC estándar."
          }
        },
        "fr-FR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD est un HUD vélo personnel et pratique conçu autour du radar arrière Coospo TR70. Les véhicules derrière vous apparaissent sur une voie radar claire avec des alertes Apple Watch, et chaque sortie est enregistrée comme entraînement Apple Santé. Compatible aussi avec les radars compatibles Garmin Varia et les capteurs de vitesse/cadence CSC standard."
          }
        },
        "it-IT" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD è un HUD personale per la bici basato sul radar posteriore Coospo TR70. I veicoli dietro di te appaiono su una corsia radar chiara con avvisi sull'Apple Watch e ogni uscita viene salvata come allenamento Apple Salute. Funziona anche con radar compatibili Garmin Varia e sensori di velocità/cadenza CSC standard."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "CycleHUD needs Bluetooth to connect to your radar and sensors. Allow it in Settings → CycleHUD → Bluetooth." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de-DE" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD benötigt Bluetooth, um sich mit deinem Radar und deinen Sensoren zu verbinden. Erlaube es in Einstellungen → CycleHUD → Bluetooth."
          }
        },
        "en-GB" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD needs Bluetooth to connect to your radar and sensors. Allow it in Settings → CycleHUD → Bluetooth."
          }
        },
        "en-US" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD needs Bluetooth to connect to your radar and sensors. Allow it in Settings → CycleHUD → Bluetooth."
          }
        },
        "es-ES" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD necesita Bluetooth para conectarse a tu radar y sensores. Permítelo en Ajustes → CycleHUD → Bluetooth."
          }
        },
        "fr-FR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD a besoin du Bluetooth pour se connecter à votre radar et à vos capteurs. Autorisez-le dans Réglages → CycleHUD → Bluetooth."
          }
        },
        "it-IT" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD ha bisogno del Bluetooth per connettersi al radar e ai sensori. Consentilo in Impostazioni → CycleHUD → Bluetooth."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "CycleHUD needs Location to record your speed, distance and route. Turn it on in Settings → CycleHUD → Location, set to “While Using the App”." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de-DE" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD benötigt den Standort, um Geschwindigkeit, Distanz und Route aufzuzeichnen. Aktiviere ihn in Einstellungen → CycleHUD → Standort, eingestellt auf „Beim Verwenden der App“."
          }
        },
        "en-GB" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD needs Location to record your speed, distance and route. Turn it on in Settings → CycleHUD → Location, set to “While Using the App”."
          }
        },
        "en-US" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD needs Location to record your speed, distance and route. Turn it on in Settings → CycleHUD → Location, set to “While Using the App”."
          }
        },
        "es-ES" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD necesita la ubicación para registrar tu velocidad, distancia y ruta. Actívala en Ajustes → CycleHUD → Ubicación, configurada en « Al usar la app »."
          }
        },
        "fr-FR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD a besoin de la localisation pour enregistrer votre vitesse, votre distance et votre itinéraire. Activez-la dans Réglages → CycleHUD → Position, réglée sur « Lorsque l'app est active »."
          }
        },
        "it-IT" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CycleHUD ha bisogno della posizione per registrare velocità, distanza e percorso. Attivala in Impostazioni → CycleHUD → Posizione, impostata su « Mentre usi l'app »."
          }
        }
      }
    },
