    "Upload rides to Strava straight from the ride summary, or automatically when a ride ends. Your Strava login stays between you and Strava — CycleHUD keeps only its upload permission, in the Keychain." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de-DE" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Lade Fahrten direkt aus der Zusammenfassung zu Strava hoch — oder automatisch am Ende jeder Fahrt. Dein Strava-Login bleibt zwischen dir und Strava; CycleHUD behält nur die Upload-Berechtigung, sicher im Schlüsselbund."
          }
        },
        "en-GB" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Upload rides to Strava straight from the ride summary, or automatically when a ride ends. Your Strava login stays between you and Strava — CycleHUD keeps only its upload permission, in the Keychain."
          }
        },
        "en-US" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Upload rides to Strava straight from the ride summary, or automatically when a ride ends. Your Strava login stays between you and Strava — CycleHUD keeps only its upload permission, in the Keychain."
          }
        },
        "es-ES" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Sube tus salidas a Strava desde el resumen, o automáticamente al terminar la salida. Tu cuenta de Strava queda entre tú y Strava — CycleHUD solo guarda el permiso de subida, en el llavero."
          }
        },
        "fr-FR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Envoyez vos sorties vers Strava depuis le résumé, ou automatiquement à la fin de chaque sortie. Votre identifiant Strava reste entre vous et Strava — CycleHUD ne conserve que l'autorisation d'envoi, dans le trousseau."
          }
        },
        "it-IT" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Carica le uscite su Strava direttamente dal riepilogo, o automaticamente a fine giro. Il tuo accesso Strava resta tra te e Strava — CycleHUD conserva solo il permesso di caricamento, nel portachiavi."
          }
        }
      }
    },
